  "stem": "<p>The equation <math><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>\u2212</mo><mn>12</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>p</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>q</mi></math> is true for all <math><mi>x</mi><mo>\u2260</mo><mo>\u2212</mo><mn>6</mn></math>, where <em>p</em> and <em>q</em> are integers. What is the value of <em>p</em> + <em>q</em>?</p>",
